title: Keen Questionere
content:
Ok people a quick questioneere, please try not to go off the subject of this thread.
If any of you have time could you please answer this questionere? it would greatly help us in develoment for the story and general construction of are game.

The idea of the game takes place when keen is 16-17, new characters and hopefully a great storyline, this questionere is mainly to build up the character of keen which we have decided to do by asking the fans off keen [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-smile.gif[/img] .

If you could copy and paste the answer part and fill in your answer accordanly that would be great.

----keen part----

Q.1.What is Billy's Favoroute food?
Q.2.Will Keen still wear converse?
Q.3.What is his fav genre of music?
Q.4.Is billy popular of not popular at school?
Q.5.A short description of Keens ideal dream girl, example human/alien, hair colour and length, skin tone, eye colour?

----game part----
Q.6.Should there be more than one weapon?
Q.7.Do you think making the game have elements of a rpg is a good idea?
Q.8.Would a level or two where you can fly the bean and bacon megarocket be a good idea?
Q.9. More action or more story?
Q.10. just to see what type of person would be intrested in the game could u leave you sex and age, you dont have to answer this one tho if you dont want to [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-smile.gif[/img] .




----Copy and Paste-----
